[{"originalPostUsername":"","postBodyContent":"","rebloggedPostURL":"https://getbacktofandomlife.tumblr.com/post/719798584415043584"},{"originalPostURL":"https://frcdburkle.tumblr.com/post/155310315775","postBodyContent":"\n                                                                        <p><small>i see a lot of people talk about willow’s sexuality and why she is a lesbian and all that\n\n((rightfully so)), but sometimes i feel like buffy’s sexuality gets sidelined just because her storyline happened on the comics instead of tv.</small></p><p><small>and it’s actually pretty important, because whether you like the comics or not it did happen, it is canon, buffy did have a relationship with a girl, even if a short one, and ignoring that is highkey queer erasure.</small></p><p><small>not to mention all the effort from people in the fandom to belittle buffy’s experiences and feelings.</small></p><p><small><i>\n\n“but buffy didn’t even like it”</i><br></small></p><figure data-orig-width=\"255\" data-orig-height=\"326\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/48f8d1a64a2d20e0f8988c100c01b5de/3116884a2f1e5f4d-65/s400x600/2e8b9fd0ceb46509f7b7c57a2b286e9dae255cdf.png\" alt=\"image\" data-orig-width=\"255\" data-orig-height=\"326\" width=\"255\" height=\"326\"></figure><figure data-orig-width=\"255\" data-orig-height=\"248\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/005af37485972e9453f1cd6fa95c684f/3116884a2f1e5f4d-54/s400x600/3aa298d561f47bd3dcd8b62c626a2d8f39e35b21.png\" alt=\"image\" data-orig-width=\"255\" data-orig-height=\"248\" width=\"255\" height=\"248\"></figure><figure data-orig-width=\"255\" data-orig-height=\"151\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/980914fd8b453cc042c1ca5c8fc86770/3116884a2f1e5f4d-9a/s400x600/a38dc888a32dc7078afbb87917690e0d33dab90c.png\" alt=\"image\" data-orig-width=\"255\" data-orig-height=\"151\" width=\"255\" height=\"151\"></figure><figure data-orig-width=\"350\" data-orig-height=\"156\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/d51c7150611c812899effa0ad96dd197/3116884a2f1e5f4d-2b/s400x600/34e23e3e636e0cbee6c5c3e4eed55a87fe06a64b.png\" alt=\"image\" data-orig-width=\"350\" data-orig-height=\"156\" width=\"350\" height=\"156\"></figure><p><small>nah, actually she liked it a lot.</small></p><p><small><i>“buffy doesn’t want to do it again”</i><br></small></p><figure data-orig-width=\"350\" data-orig-height=\"96\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/dff4f90c87e952e13c0cf522e0e3e8c3/3116884a2f1e5f4d-ba/s400x600/a01a53821508087baeddf8398000b5451f707d82.png\" alt=\"image\" data-orig-width=\"350\" data-orig-height=\"96\" width=\"350\" height=\"96\"></figure><p><small>spoiler: buffy does it again.</small></p><p><small><i>“buffy’s not really attracted to satsu, it just happened”</i><br></small></p><figure data-orig-width=\"255\" data-orig-height=\"102\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/25ddfba96a64b27d58635acb68505394/3116884a2f1e5f4d-ed/s400x600/21f493a7ce498b6cef005662d7fdec4a39f53b69.png\" alt=\"image\" data-orig-width=\"255\" data-orig-height=\"102\" width=\"255\" height=\"102\"></figure><figure data-orig-width=\"255\" data-orig-height=\"102\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/81ac0d87a8408b31327e1b04c1e3eef8/3116884a2f1e5f4d-b7/s400x600/08b4b5aaaa2eb36c65cc81be4570ab2ece6dd1fb.png\" alt=\"image\" data-orig-width=\"255\" data-orig-height=\"102\" width=\"255\" height=\"102\"></figure><figure data-orig-width=\"255\" data-orig-height=\"391\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/deac1c00b319c16a8a29e29a5098803a/3116884a2f1e5f4d-3b/s400x600/cca1e1f67ac71b7149fd24447460c81db1469fea.png\" alt=\"image\" data-orig-width=\"255\" data-orig-height=\"391\" width=\"255\" height=\"391\"></figure><p><small>ha.</small></p><p><small><i>“buffy said she isn’t gay.”</i><br></small></p><figure data-orig-width=\"600\" data-orig-height=\"768\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/e2e1cf5bb4903f7e25b2ba03b36dc074/3116884a2f1e5f4d-c4/s640x960/bec4431e9b39cdb484c158877605ea44ac94702c.png\" alt=\"image\" data-orig-width=\"600\" data-orig-height=\"768\" width=\"600\" height=\"768\"></figure><p><small>funny you say that bc the people who say buffy’s not gay are entirely of the <i>Not-Buffy</i> variety, they were her friends believing they have a say on buffy’s sexuality and love life as they’ve done since the very beginning of the show. Buffy herself never really talks about it after what happened. moreover, buffy not identifying herself as a lesbian does not mean she’s not queer. just because the buffyverse refuses to acknowledge the words bisexual and pansexual, doesn’t mean that these sexualities don’t exist.</small></p><p><small>buffy’s relationship with satsu didn’t go forward, yeah, but that had nothing to do with any of these bullshit excuses. it had everything to do with buffy’s inability to connect to people on an emotional level ((which is something that’s been explored since season 4)) and her fear of putting satsu in danger.</small></p><figure data-orig-width=\"350\" data-orig-height=\"101\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/b3efe9a340cfbdcefec2681a17eb3f8b/3116884a2f1e5f4d-c9/s400x600/be3aa45088b671018b2b52b6eb538559f49d0ebe.png\" alt=\"image\" data-orig-width=\"350\" data-orig-height=\"101\" width=\"350\" height=\"101\"></figure><figure data-orig-width=\"255\" data-orig-height=\"250\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/90a5a35479462fde728c03c044bfd59e/3116884a2f1e5f4d-53/s400x600/6a7d7b38d500849b9daf1db5a15d39d0855011d7.png\" alt=\"image\" data-orig-width=\"255\" data-orig-height=\"250\" width=\"255\" height=\"250\"></figure><figure data-orig-width=\"350\" data-orig-height=\"101\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/fc09d821b41523836f14c948cdc9507c/3116884a2f1e5f4d-d5/s400x600/7fa1900fa8f250b4836bb5fa1697448d39fe6fc1.png\" alt=\"image\" data-orig-width=\"350\" data-orig-height=\"101\" width=\"350\" height=\"101\"></figure><figure data-orig-width=\"255\" data-orig-height=\"403\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/e98401bc020865423a936d3145e88e34/3116884a2f1e5f4d-99/s400x600/98cdfdffb846b475a45636c54b82e80e23d86db0.png\" alt=\"image\" data-orig-width=\"255\" data-orig-height=\"403\" width=\"255\" height=\"403\"></figure><p><small>there’s a lot more to be said if you want to include buffy’s relationship with faith and all the text and subtext that comes from that but i wanted to focus on that specific storyline. and what that storyline tells us is that yes, buffy anne summers is most likely bisexual. accept it, love it.</small></p>\n                                                                    ","rebloggedPostURL":"https://getbacktofandomlife.tumblr.com/post/719798564691247104/frcdburkle-i-see-a-lot-of-people-talk-about"},{"originalPostUsername":"","postBodyContent":"","rebloggedPostURL":"https://getbacktofandomlife.tumblr.com/post/719798554701512704"},{"originalPostURL":"https://jermainecoles.tumblr.com/post/154905567964","postBodyContent":"\n                                                                    <p></p><blockquote><div><small><a href=\"https://href.li/?https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UQIs5M78z64\">A true smartass.</a></small></div></blockquote>\n                                                                ","rebloggedPostURL":"https://getbacktofandomlife.tumblr.com/post/719798552063262720/jermainecolesa-true-smartass"},{"originalPostUsername":"","postBodyContent":"","rebloggedPostURL":"https://getbacktofandomlife.tumblr.com/post/719798549345452032/me-always-wants-books-also-me-already-owns-40"},{"originalPostURL":"https://greyjoie.tumblr.com/post/79936472298","postBodyContent":"\n                                                                        <p>it sucks teen wolf ended after season 2</p>\n                                                                    ","rebloggedPostURL":"https://getbacktofandomlife.tumblr.com/post/719798546676727808/greyjoie-it-sucks-teen-wolf-ended-after-season-2"},{"originalPostURL":"https://petuniaevans.tumblr.com/post/155183776285","postBodyContent":"\n                                                                    <p><b><a href=\"http://petuniaevans.tumblr.com/tagged/mmc\">Make Me Choose: </a><i>Drarry</i></b><i> or <strike>Scorbus </strike></i>- for anonymous</p><p><i>“Malfoy was screaming and holding Harry so tightly it hurt.”&nbsp;</i><br></p>\n                                                                ","rebloggedPostURL":"https://getbacktofandomlife.tumblr.com/post/719798544007102464/petuniaevans-make-me-choose-drarry-or-scorbus"},{"originalPostURL":"https://petuniaevans.tumblr.com/post/155217945675","postBodyContent":"\n                                                                    <p><b><a href=\"http://petuniaevans.tumblr.com/tagged/mmc\">Make Me Choose:</a> <i>Petunia</i></b><i> or <strike>Dudley Dursley</strike> </i>- for <a class=\"tumblelog\" href=\"https://tmblr.co/mC-2lRBQ0yr_RAwb1dspOJw\">@pessimisticbee</a>&nbsp;</p><p>\n\n“<i>She stopped and looked back. For a moment, Harry had the strangest feeling that she wanted to say something to him: she gave him an odd, tremulous look and seemed to teeter on the edge of speech.”</i><br></p>\n                                                                ","rebloggedPostURL":"https://getbacktofandomlife.tumblr.com/post/719798541344800768/petuniaevans-make-me-choose-petunia-or-dudley"},{"originalPostURL":"https://trialsofapollo.tumblr.com/post/146284708845","postBodyContent":"\n                                                                    <p><small>I thought about the first time I’d visited Mount Olympus, back when I was twelve. Annabeth and Grover hadn’t been with me then. I was glad they were with me now. I had a feeling it might be our last adventure together.</small>&nbsp;</p>\n                                                                ","rebloggedPostURL":"https://getbacktofandomlife.tumblr.com/post/719798507794464768/trialsofapollo-i-thought-about-the-first-time"},{"originalPostURL":"https://julliettewarner.tumblr.com/post/150743154936","postBodyContent":"\n                                                                    <p></p><blockquote><p><small>Ron had a fit of gallantry and insisted that Hermione sleep on the cushions from the sofa, so that her silhouette was raised above his. Her arm curved to the floor, her finger’s inches from Ron’s. Harry wondered whether <b>they had fallen asleep holding hands.</b></small></p></blockquote>\n                                                                ","rebloggedPostURL":"https://getbacktofandomlife.tumblr.com/post/719798493221453824/julliettewarner-ron-had-a-fit-of-gallantry-and"}]